# FocusFlow

FocusFlow is a modern productivity web application designed to help users manage tasks, track progress, and improve focus using a built-in Pomodoro timer.

It is built with a scalable architecture and includes task management, analytics, dark mode, and full data export/import support — making it ready for future SaaS expansion.

---

## ✨ Features

### 🗂 Task Management
- Create, edit, and delete tasks
- Set priority (Low / Medium / High)
- Add due dates
- Mark tasks as completed
- Search and filter tasks

### 📊 Dashboard
- Task statistics
- Progress tracking
- Overdue tracking
- Session insights

### ⏱ Focus Timer
- Pomodoro-style timer
- Customizable work & break durations
- Session tracking history
- Visual progress ring

### 💾 Data Management
- Export data as JSON
- Import data from JSON
- Local data persistence

### 🌙 UI & Experience
- Dark / Light mode
- Responsive design
- Clean and modern interface

